### Hotel Food Order Page

#### Overview
The hotel food order page is a simple and elegant web interface designed to make it easy for hotel guests to browse the menu and place their food orders online. The page is built using HTML for structure and basic CSS for styling, offering a clean and user-friendly experience.

#### Features
1. **Menu Display**: The page includes a well-organized menu section that showcases various food items. Each item is presented with a name, description, price, and an accompanying image to help guests make informed choices.

2. **Order Form**: An intuitive order form allows guests to select their desired food items, specify the quantity, and provide any special instructions. The form is designed to be straightforward and easy to use.

3. **Responsive Design**: Basic CSS ensures that the page is responsive, providing a seamless experience across different devices, from smartphones to desktops.

#### HTML Structure
The HTML structure is neatly organized into several key sections:

- **Header**: Includes the hotel name and navigation links for easy access to other pages.
- **Menu Section**: Displays the food items categorized into different sections for easy browsing.
- **Order Form**: Allows guests to place their orders by selecting items, specifying quantities, and adding special instructions.
- **Footer**: Contains contact information and links to the hotel's social media profiles.

#### CSS Styling
Basic CSS is used to create a visually appealing layout. Key styling elements include:

- **Typography**: Clean and readable fonts are used to enhance the user experience.
- **Layout**: Flexbox and grid layout techniques are employed to structure the content.
- **Colors and Themes**: A consistent color scheme is applied to match the hotel's branding.
- **Buttons and Forms**: Styled buttons and form inputs improve usability and interactivity.

#### Example Code

**HTML:**
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hotel Food Order</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Hotel Name</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="#">Home</a>
            <a href="#">Menu</a>
            <a href="#">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section id="menu">
            <h2>Our Menu</h2>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="path/to/image.jpg" alt="Food Item">
                <h3>Item Name</h3>
                <p>Description of the food item.</p>
                <p>Price: $10</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Repeat for other menu items -->
        </section>
        <section id="order">
            <h2>Place Your Order</h2>
            <form>
                <label for="item">Select Item:</label>
                <select id="item" name="item">
                    <option value="item1">Item 1</option>
                    <option value="item2">Item 2</option>
                </select>
                <label for="quantity">Quantity:</label>
                <input type="number" id="quantity" name="quantity" min="1" max="10">
                <label for="instructions">Special Instructions:</label>
                <textarea id="instructions" name="instructions"></textarea>
                <button type="submit">Order Now</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>Contact us at: info@hotelname.com</p>
        <p>Follow us on social media</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
```

**CSS:**
```css
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
}

header {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 1em 0;
    text-align: center;
}

header nav a {
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 1em;
    text-decoration: none;
}

main {
    padding: 2em;
}

#menu, #order {
    margin-bottom: 2em;
}

.menu-item {
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 1em;
    margin: 1em 0;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.menu-item img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

form {
    background-color: #fff;
    padding: 1em;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

form label {
    display: block;
    margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em;
}

form input, form select, form textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.5em;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
}

button {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 1em 2em;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

button:hover {
    background-color: #555;
}

footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1em 0;
}
```

